content: Hey,Lbank delist: NKPLTPCPAEAXLCLANDDSOPlease, where can I do a withraw for these coins? I mean that platforms or anything...Thanks,

comments.author: _act_
comments.body: Coin Coingecko, type the name of the coin. If you see the coin, click on it and click on exchangs. You will see the lists of exchanges the coin your searched for are listed and how the trading volume is. On Coinmarketcap, do the same, but you will see 'market' instead of exchanges. Click on market and you will see the lists of exchanges the coin is traded.
